import styled from "styled-components"
import Annoucement from "../components/Annoucement"
import Footer from "../components/Footer"
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar"

const Container = styled.div``
const Cart = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
        <Navbar/>
        <Annoucement/>
        Cart
        <Footer/>
    </Container>
  )
}

export default Cart
